snippet.title: Hyperspace Colonization Trailer [Android Game]
snippet.description:
Gather resources from planets, upgrade your own spaceship, found new fertile planets to colonize and reach the boundary of the universe. Find suitable planets for humanity will not be easy.

Explore the procedural universe in this strategic-puzzle space game. Create a colossal galactic empire (or at least try to survive) in Hyperspace Colonization.

Download it on google play store:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.giudark.teleport_in_the_universe
